-
  const phone = '+7 (495) 782-28-93';
  const data = {
    count: '8',
    totalPrice: '1 444 128',
    discount: '288 128',
    totalPriceWithDiscount: '1 156 000',
  };

footer.cart-footer(data-component='cart-footer')
  div.cart-footer__container.container
    div.cart-footer__wrapper
      div.cart-price
        div.cart-price__items
          div.cart-price__item
            div.cart-price__item_left Ваш заказ:
            div.cart-price__item_right
              =data.count
              | ТОВАРОВ
          div.cart-price__item
            div.cart-price__item_left Товары на сумму:
            div.cart-price__item_right
              = data.totalPrice
              span.cart-price__item_small РУБ
          div.cart-price__item
            div.cart-price__item_left Скидка:
            div.cart-price__item_right
              = data.discount
              span.cart-price__item_small РУБ
          div.cart-price__separator
          div.cart-price__item
            div.cart-price__item_left Итого:
            div.cart-price__item_right
              = data.totalPriceWithDiscount
              span.cart-price__item_small РУБ
      button.cart-footer__order-button.order-button Перейти к Оформлению
    div.cart-footer__bottom
      div.cart-footer__bottom-part
        a.cart-footer__link(href=`tel:${phone}`)= phone
        a.cart-footer__link.cart-footer__link_underline(href='mailto:mk@tigon.ru') mk@tigon.ru
        a.cart-footer__link.cart-footer__link_underline(href=`tel:${phone}`) Обратный звонок
      div.cart-footer__sep
      a.cart-footer__link.cart-footer__link_underline(href='#') О доставке и оплате